GeneralComments: Blink network does not maintain the equipment, based on their contract with the Town of Oro Valley. Spaces are NOT reserved for EVs, so it is likely that either a charger will be out of service or physical inaccessible. Two of 3 were non-functioning as of 2/15/17.
